As with all self- testing, users may be provided with links or contact details to access additional support, such as telephone hotlines or instructional videos” (WHO, 2016) • In addition to reporting the total number of HIV self-test kits distributed to individuals, the HTS_SELF indicator includes several disaggregates to characterize aspects of distribution.
